---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Materials" description="Open course notes from graduate and undergraduate methods training – Felipe Lamarca">
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <header>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-2">Materials</h1>
      <p class="text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Open notes from graduate and undergraduate methods training</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2 class="section-title">Course Notes</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark mb-6">Notes and code from methods courses I have taken. Shared openly for other researchers and students.</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="subsection-title">Graduate</h3>
          <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
            <div class="py-4">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Lego III</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">IESP-UERJ · 2026.1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
                  <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Lego-III" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
                  <a href="https://felipelamarca.com/Lego-III/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website →</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Causal inference: potential outcomes, DAGs, and identification strategies.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="py-4">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Lego II</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">IESP-UERJ · 2025.2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
                  <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Lego-II" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
                  <a href="https://felipelamarca.com/Lego-II/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website →</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Linear regression models and extensions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="py-4">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Lego I</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">IESP-UERJ · 2025.1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
                  <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Lego-I" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
                  <a href="https://felipelamarca.com/Lego-I/" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website →</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Quantitative social science: data analysis, research design, probability, and inference.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="subsection-title">Undergraduate</h3>
          <div class="divide-y divide-border dark:divide-border-dark">
            <div class="py-4">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Deep Learning</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">FGV EMAp · 2023.2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
                  <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Deep-Learning" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Foundations of NNs, CNNs, LSTMs, GANs, Transformers, transfer learning, and autoencoders.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="py-4">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline sm:justify-between gap-1 mb-1">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-baseline gap-2">
                  <span class="font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Machine Learning</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-ink-muted dark:text-ink-muted-dark">FGV EMAp · 2023.1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-4 text-sm">
                  <a href="https://github.com/felipelmc/Machine-Learning" class="link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub →</a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-ink-secondary dark:text-ink-secondary-dark">Probabilistic machine learning, mixture models, and approximate Bayesian inference.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
